{
  "stem": "2804.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- we had to help these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They needed us so badly, we had to do what we could, just to think of ourselves or--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we would talk about it and help each other and just say, we just have to take care of them, do what we could.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They've been through so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because about a week before or a couple-- I think even a couple of days before, a train load had come on the rail.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a railing in back-- in the back of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found out that about 1,000 people were jammed into these boxcars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when it reached Dachau, about maybe 500 people were left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rest were dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when they got into Dachau, the soldiers that had gone in had opened up these boxcars and took the people that were there out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was a couple of days before we came in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they had been there maybe three, three, four years, some of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it must've been about three- three years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Survived.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that they-- were working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We really-- we really couldn't, because, as I said, there was so much to do, day and night, just trying to save them or to take care of them, and then the language difficulty and trying to make them understand what we were doing, that it was really difficult to have really stories or anything else.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just wanted to get them out of there and into the clean barracks, into a clean bed, and--",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
